tasks.description:
Update the `RunResult` type (likely in `src/pipeline/types.ts`) to carry review information so callers can display it.

1. Add an optional `reviewSummary` field to `RunResult`:
   ```ts
   reviewSummary?: {
     ran: boolean;
     passed: boolean;
     totalFindings: number;
     blockingFindings: number;
     threshold: string;
     findings: ReviewFinding[]; // reuse or import whatever type telesis review already returns
   }
   ```
2. Import or reuse the existing finding type from the review business logic package (e.g. `src/review/`) — do not duplicate the type.
3. Update the CLI run command's output handler to print the review summary when `reviewSummary.ran` is true — show finding counts and whether it passed or blocked.
4. No orchestrator changes yet.
